article.description: — Jayden Martinez had a career-high 33 points plus 14 rebounds as New Hampshire got past Quinnipiac 84-69 on Tuesday.
article.headline: Martinez lifts New Hampshire past Quinnipiac 84-69
article.linkText: Martinez lifts New Hampshire past Quinnipiac 84-69
article.story: DURHAM, N.H. -- — Jayden Martinez had a career-high 33 points plus 14 rebounds as New Hampshire got past Quinnipiac 84-69 on Tuesday. Martinez made 13 of 15 shots. Blondeau Tchoukuiegno had 13 points and six rebounds for New Hampshire (2-2). Josh Hopkins added 11 points and Nick Guadarrama had five assists. Dezi Jones had 19 points for the Bobcats (3-2). Matt Balanc and Tyrese Williams each had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
